    "like_count": "23",
    "media_id": "54906777321697660",
    "parent_id": "parentid-e1f3a8cf1736",
    "text": "Luc that redfish Elise is holding is almost as big as she is 😂 nice work out on the flats",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-29T07:17:58+00:00",
    "user_id": "27446700178170503",
    "username": "luc"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "67372814184201292",
    "like_count": "8",
    "media_id": "90006067941454490",
    "parent_id": "parentid-d687ab5f1be4",
    "text": "That's Elise right there — she's got your mother's eyes and my stubborn chin. Hang that one up, son.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-28T13:49:18+00:00",
    "user_id": "15432004837463993",
    "username": "marcel"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "92628546177916752",
    "like_count": "24",
    "media_id": "21148328441612197",
    "parent_id": "parentid-2daeff9661cd",
    "text": "That's Elise right there 😄 Looks just like Luc did at that age. Send that one to Diane, she'll lose her mind.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T14:37:55+00:00",
    "user_id": "86851189562416738",
    "username": "ashley"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "87931361148744463",
    "like_count": "10",
    "media_id": "76264845013278290",
    "parent_id": "parentid-ad1ffb5563c2",
    "text": "That redfish mount finally came in for the shop wall. Grandma Diane says it looks mean 😄 You'd love it Elise.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-28T17:30:56+00:00",
    "user_id": "73653815546862492",
    "username": "elise"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "86225930177099494",
    "like_count": "7",
    "media_id": "76458625180464796",
    "parent_id": "parentid-f473270981de",
    "text": "That redfish is a solid 24\" easy. You catch that off Bayport or further south?",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T12:39:39+00:00",
    "user_id": "28379802856917665",
    "username": "beau"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "88952417054761858",
    "like_count": "20",
    "media_id": "15375547785314223",
    "parent_id": "parentid-620c8b4d822f",
    "text": "Denise, Elise's got Luc's exact same grin in that photo. Kills me every time 😄",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-24T10:01:01+00:00",
    "user_id": "84211750343769178",
    "username": "denise"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "22700870917888997",
    "like_count": "8",
    "media_id": "36281527725438323",
    "parent_id": "parentid-00f8686a9070",
    "text": "Finished the parlor build last night. You'd have something to say about that headstock, I know it.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-24T21:06:10+00:00",
    "user_id": "83908732967723124",
    "username": "henry"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "62140414210208533",
    "like_count": "5",
    "media_id": "23107526762521474",
    "parent_id": "parentid-af58f005f5b8",
    "text": "That redfish Luc caught off the Lucky Strike yesterday — told you Bayport flats were holding. Kid's got the touch.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-26T18:41:45+00:00",
    "user_id": "61734737830098207",
    "username": "russ"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "49019698591324457",
    "like_count": "24",
    "media_id": "78231135241459997",
    "parent_id": "parentid-334945a2b129",
    "text": "Nolan that tarpon is bigger than anything we pulled out of Bayport all April. Luc's gonna be sick he missed it 😂",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-29T21:19:09+00:00",
    "user_id": "67419146673083558",
    "username": "nolan"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "36832497001456845",
    "like_count": "8",
    "media_id": "85033000556093445",
    "parent_id": "parentid-da0241a9b83f",
    "text": "Claire that redfish Elise caught off Bayport Tuesday — send that to Luc. Kid's been asking if she's ready for a real cha",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-19T19:23:24+00:00",
    "user_id": "40990500143327177",
    "username": "claire"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "28897881257300054",
    "like_count": "12",
    "media_id": "69903823552772222",
    "parent_id": "parentid-f47c4462eabe",
    "text": "David that's Elise holding her first keeper redfish off the Lucky Strike — Diane caught that grin on camera 📸",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-26T01:32:27+00:00",
    "user_id": "90603647092539466",
    "username": "david"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "75935770554391475",
    "like_count": "24",
    "media_id": "73333479677784813",
    "parent_id": "parentid-a5bd8f94a09c",
    "text": "Paul that's gotta be Bayport pier — Diane and I walked that stretch last Sunday. Small world, doc 😄",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-26T01:18:18+00:00",
    "user_id": "81828500238923255",
    "username": "paul"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "75861677781718401",
    "like_count": "4",
    "media_id": "20123639387451203",
    "parent_id": "parentid-a0c1807fe590",
    "text": "Renee, sent that photo of the spot on my forearm. Gets a lot of sun out on the water — Bayport charter life. Worth comin",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-29T12:46:10+00:00",
    "user_id": "78269264107735678",
    "username": "renee"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
